<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694322>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 44. Female genitalia of Siberian Ennominae. A—Alcis extinctaria; B—A. deversata; C—Abraxas grossulariata; D—A. karafutonis; E—A. sylvata; F—Calcaritis pallida; G—Lomaspilis marginata; H—L. nigrita; I—Isturgia arenacearia. A, B—sterigma and posterior part of the corpus bursae. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4694322/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4694274>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 28. Male genitalia of Siberian Ennominae.A, B—Isturgia arenacearia; C–E—Narraga fasciolaria; F–H—Digrammia rippertaria; I–K—Macaria circumflexaria; L–N—M. wauaria. A, D, F, I, L—genital segment; B, E, G, J, M—phallos; C—valva; H, K, N—VIII abdominal sternite. Scale bar—1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4694274/files/figure.png" .
